  "title": "Rideable Ravagers",
  "description": "You can tame and ride Ravagers",
  "body": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> <a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> <a href=\"https://minecraftservers.org/server/642659\"><img title=\"phobos.mcserv.fun\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Fminecraft-server-status-badge.vercel.app%2Fapi%2Fserver%2Fphobos.mcserv.fun%3Fport%3D25565&amp;label=Phobos MC server&amp;style=for-the-badge\" /></a> </strong></h5>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rideable Ravagers is a mod that makes it possible for you to ride ravagers after feeding them the Ravagers Cake</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1F6I0wn.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"528\" height=\"264\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rZfuEqT.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"527\" height=\"236\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Ravagers Cake</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The mobs that spawn in a raid are attracted to this block and want to eat it. If a Ravager eats it becomes rideable but if any other mob eats it dies.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OwlQlrB.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"252\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Dfgc1Dr.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"563\" height=\"252\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VI91kWF.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"474\" height=\"268\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FQLov3P.png\" width=\"301\" height=\"201\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/5968/5968732.png\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" width=\"30\" /></a> Patrons:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/zoopla2323\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span class=\"sc-ieecCq gLfHQe\" data-tag=\"user-details-full-name\">Linkyboy Hendrie</span></a></li>\n</ul>",
